	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=119627><span id=Sage>Kedr</span></a><br><b><span id=Sage>Sage</span></b><br><span id=notbold>59 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.96]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Ever wonder what a weapon will hit for?<br><br>Level bonus = (level - 25 / 2)<br><br>Max damage = (weapon skill + strenght / 100) x (weapon damage + level bonus)<br><br>Example:&nbsp;&nbsp;level 40 Warrior, skill of 200, strenght of 150.<br><br>( 200 + 150 / 100) x (21 + 7) = 98 damage<br><br>This does not include critical hits or crippling blows.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
